  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Critical Prerequisite: Level 8+, Heavy Armor Mastery </p><p>While you are wearing heavy armor with which you are proficient, you gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Twice per Long Rest, when a hostile creature would score a critical hit against you, you can treat it as a normal hit.</p><p> You regain one use of this effect, on a short rest.</p><p>• You gain 5 DR (Damage reduction) vs the damage applied from a Critical hit.</p><p>• When an allied creature within 10 feet of you would be hit by a critical attack, you may spend your reaction to redirect the attack to yourself.</p><p> You can do this once per initiative.</p><p></p>",
